text: chaur anak pol tha pitabrakd nasa mcheasa robsakhnhom baek touleay nouv leaphosakkar champoh anaknea del trong mean chetnea ampikhnhom robsa trong haey trong ka kbetakbiet champoh ke der . haey avei b ndich kadaoy del puok anak ban brichcheak noh ku trong nung tabasnang vea vinh . haey trong chea anak bratan leaphosakkar da la bamphot
